{"tid":161923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"論壇禁採訪　記者不滿離場","createTime":"2017-03-19T01:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T04:18:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4218a5686295cee745774337750860cbf6069692","tid":161923,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T01:02:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19962980&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170319\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19962980%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170319&d=pX%2F9NM0RDLHEoMpKo%2B7ToaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=27403c1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19962980%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170319&h=a90a83b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19962980&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170319</a><br />\n<br />\n論壇禁採訪　記者不滿離場<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n林鄭昨出席建測界論壇，傳媒到場才「被通知」閉門進行，被拒入內。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首候選人林鄭月娥昨出席建築、測量、都市規劃及園境界論壇，獲邀採訪的傳媒到場才「被通知」論壇閉門進行，「members only（只限會員）」，主辦單位更以保安為由，不容記者進場，也不設採訪及攝影，着自行觀看facebook直播。最後記者集體離場以示不滿。<br />\n<br />\n到場始「通知」閉門進行<br />\n<br />\n論壇於調景嶺香港知專設計學院舉行，昨早港鐵站外四周約有20名警員駐守，附近也停泊多輛警車。論壇昨早約11時舉行，大批傳媒早已到場等候，惟林鄭月娥經側門進場，未露一面。登記處職員稱不能入內採訪，可在房間收看論壇facebook直播，但房內只得枱椅。<br />\n其後香港建築師學會副會長何文堯出來回應，起初態度強硬，指已通知是閉門論壇，但記者質疑為何仍發採訪通知，他即面露不悅指，「寫明members only」，並稱因保安問題，記者不能進場，他在主持論壇開首更指，要處理場外記者「起哄」，稱無法接受記者入內採訪的要求，「當然會俾人鬧啦」。<br />\n林鄭競選辦人員指，可在論壇環節之間安排林鄭見傳媒，「傾一傾偈，影一影相」。但記者強調，林鄭與建測界交流討論才是採訪重點，而非林鄭跟傳媒放話，最後集體離場以示不滿。記者翻看採訪通知，全文沒標示「members only」及閉門進行，而林鄭事後稱，自己立場是「客隨主便」，又稱曾對主辦機構說，若有邀傳媒到場，可讓傳媒採訪部份論壇，然後才閉門交流。<br />\n■記者王家文"},{"pid":"479f1a96db904c52afa6678a2f99e74d310afd50","tid":161923,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T01:04:45.000Z","msg":"林鄭昨出席建測界論壇，傳媒到場才「被通知」閉門進行，被拒入內。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170319/large/19la2p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170319%2Flarge%2F19la2p4.jpg&h=c251935c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5be71db99d16c8d64f720b0665bd1ce102944339","tid":161923,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T01:06:47.000Z","msg":"吹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d69bbd236a6a99b7b26b2de1736d9249d484c5ab","tid":161923,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T01:08:40.000Z","msg":"做俾有票自己人睇就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e8d849a5b506c4ec2a7dc7f59e77a6129c947b","tid":161923,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T01:11:56.000Z","msg":"都勝硬 在乎你地班記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國一聲令下 咪又係爭住含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5aeb63a01450d3da23bd32aa38709c963d1827c","tid":161923,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T01:14:27.000Z","msg":"保安理由....原來記者咁危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83555716c8160dd79273fd297f38c57b45c5bf79","tid":161923,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T01:31:13.000Z","msg":"食屎啦建築師學會奶林鄭<br />\n唔怪得曾胡唔去<br />\n睇怕都係助攻論壇"},{"pid":"9d049efb20620749ac0ec5cbaa311678c7a4695b","tid":161923,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T01:38:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食屎啦建築師學會奶林鄭<br />\n唔怪得曾胡唔去<br />\n睇怕都係助攻論壇</blockquote><br />\n胡官中過一次伏邊會去<img src=\"/as